4 A. The Oklahoma Department of Human Services is hereby directed
5 to submit a request to the United States Department of Agriculture
6 Food and Nutrition Service for a waiver to exclude the following
7 categories of items from being eligible for purchase using
8 Supplemental Nutrition Assistance Program (SNAP) benefits within the
9 state of Oklahoma:
10 1. Candy, as defined in Section 1352 of Title 68 of the
11 Oklahoma Statutes; and
12 2. Soft drinks, as defined in Section 1352 of Title 68 of the
13 Oklahoma Statutes.
14 B. The waiver request shall include:
15 1. Justification for excluding candy and soft drinks from SNAP
16 purchases based on public health and economic impacts;
17 2. A proposed implementation plan, including retailer
18 compliance, participant education, and enforcement mechanisms; and
19 3. Any additional supporting data demonstrating the need for
20 this reform.
